description:
Toolroom Knights Ibiza (2014) 

                    House, Dance, Club | Toolroom Longplayer

              320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2014 | 09:17:33 | 1.25 Gb


Toolroom Knights Ibiza 2014' encapsulates the vibe & relives the atmosphere from the weekly parties, blending a staggering 50 full-length summer anthems hand-picked by Toolroom Knights residents Audiowhores, Rene Amesz & Prok & Fitch spread across 3 lovingly crafted DJ mixes. Kicking off the mixes on a deeper tip are the Audiowhores who bring blissed-out Balearic beats infused with cool cuts & killer hooks. Rene Amesz picks up the pace with Mix 2, infusing his trademark House sound, mixed with Toolroom favourites & recent summer smashes. Delivering the third & final mix are label favourites Prok & Fitch, rounding off the comp with pure, undiluted Tech House, pounding basslines & underground beats. 

Featuring tracks from Audiojack, Doorly, Copy Paste Soul, Rafa Barrios, Coyu, Erik Hagleton, Harry Romero, Riva Starr, Kaiserdisco, Pirupa, My Digital Enemy, Filterheadz, Deetron & Sonny Fodera and spanning a multitude of genres, 'Toolroom Knights Ibiza 2014' is your essential guide to this year's party season with hits to see you through from sunset to sunrise.
